    + Attributes (Message)

### Send a message [POST /inboxes/{inbox_id}/messages]

Sends a new message from an inbox. It will create a new conversation, if you want to reply to an existing conversation, refer to [Send a reply](#reference/conversations/conversation-resource/send-a-reply).

+ Parameters
    + inbox_id (string, required) - Id or address of the inbox from which to send the message

+ Request (application/json)
    <!-- include(../includes/request_header.apib) -->
    + Attributes (Outbound new message)

