### Receive an incoming message [POST /inboxes/{inbox_id}/incoming_messages]

Simulate the reception of an incoming message. This endpoint can be used with [custom inboxes](#reference/custom-inboxes) **ONLY**.

+ Parameters
    + inbox_id (string, required) - Id or address of the requested inbox

